Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:50.29,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.36,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I'm with Akeuchi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:55.09,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel my worries grow lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:56.38,Default,Ozaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.61,Default,Ozaki,0000,0000,0000,,Bonavuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:59.51,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Mativuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.76,Default,Yao,0000,0000,0000,,That's seriously {\i1}so{\i0} weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:04.15,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:05.89,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally normal out in space!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.41,Default,Yao,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing, Yu-chan the alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.78,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You don't believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:11.64,Default,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:13.12,Default,Group,0000,0000,0000,,Bonavuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.65,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Mativuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:17.40,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,When did everyone start using it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.75,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,It really is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:21.82,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san really is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:26.16,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,She's an alien, but she can \Nfit in with everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:28.26,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan! Umika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:31.54,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Haruno!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.54,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:34.97,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Bonavuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:36.29,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Mativuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:39.80,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,This is my classmate, Haruno Takaragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:43.18,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,She's our class vice president.\NShe's cheerful and outgoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:46.30,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Bonavuu to you too, Umika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:54.55,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,She's a very nice Earthling who will even \Nstrike up a conversation with someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.06,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:05:03.82,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't managed to talk to Takaragi-san a \Nsingle time since she first approached me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.39,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:07.58,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hand in your Japanese \Nassignment from yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:08.79,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I completely forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:11.45,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Emihara-sensei was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.26,DefaultTop,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.68,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:16.50,DefaultTop,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That's our math assignment from last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.42,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.46,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,As I am now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:23.46,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm powerless to bring not only myself, \Nbut also Akeuchi-san into outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:24.84,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:27.70,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask the two of you something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.77,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:30.60,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:34.35,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,did you two go in the lighthouse on the cape?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:35.73,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(111,1)\an7\fnTimes New Roman\bord2\c&H212522&\3c&H52534E&}PUBLIC ENTRY PROHIBITED\NBEYOND THIS POINT\N{\fs16}Coast Guard Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.23,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\bord2\c&H211A12&\fnTimes New Roman\3c&HAC8B7B&}PUBLIC ENTRY PROHIBITED BEYOND THIS POINT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:40.61,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's time for class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:43.35,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pick this up again later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:44.61,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:51.12,Default,Kaneda,0000,0000,0000,,The following year, an imperial censor \Nfrom Chen by the name of Yuan Can...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:53.37,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.2\fs12\fnTimes New Roman\c&H1E1619&\fax0.33\pos(166,248)}Modern Japanese
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:53.37,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:57.50,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san is using the \Nlighthouse as her secret base.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.50,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone were to find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.89,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Scary folks will come investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.63,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,They'll find out that \NAkeuchi-san is an alien,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:08.13,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,and then they'll capture her, tie her up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:11.07,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Save me, Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:14.39,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to dissect Akeuchi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:18.52,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I need to make sure that no one \Ndiscovers Akeuchi-san's secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:19.40,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.2\fs12\fnTimes New Roman\c&H1E1619&\fax0.33\pos(177.5,259)}Modern Japanese
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:19.40,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Konohoshi, you read next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:22.20,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Konohoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.73,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Umika-chan, she's calling your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:29.21,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Not paying attention in my class?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:31.78,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Some nerve you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.48,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It starts on line 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:37.97,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:39.79,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,O-One night...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:43.44,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Konohoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.80,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Good job reading everything so carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.79,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Have some more confidence next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:50.74,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Shiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:51.55,Default,Shiki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:54.93,DefaultTop,Shiki,0000,0000,0000,,Just as it appeared that the tiger \Nwas about to spring upon Yuan Can...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:54.93,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Umika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.43,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You gave it your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:05.83,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to thank Takaragi-san \Nthis time, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:08.69,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.41,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:21.12,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I need to stop Akeuchi-san from \Ntalking about the lighthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:23.52,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Umika?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:27.38,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:33.51,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(531,1)\an7\bord0\blur1\p1\c&HF0F3F1&\pos(44,30)\fscx126\fscy255}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.75,0:07:33.51,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(531,1)\fs20\an7\c&H212522&\pos(44,80)}The lighthouse\N\Nis supposed\N\Nto be off-limits,\N\Nso we should\N\Nkeep it a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:31.84,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Some kinda new game?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.51,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:35.26,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.77,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You two really are so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:39.79,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,We sure are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:41.31,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Why, just yesterday, at my base—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:43.03,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,"Base"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.26,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:46.52,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.28,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:55.16,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\bord0\blur1\p1\pos(97.5,272.5)\c&HF0F3F1&\fscx443\fscy50}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.28,0:07:55.16,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\c&H181C19&\pos(320,272)}If word of the base gets out,\Nyou could end up dissected!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:55.16,DefaultTop,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:57.91,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, right now, I live in a lighthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.91,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.21,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Li...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:03.05,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Live in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:06.56,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The bright flashes of light \Ncan be a real pain, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:07.71,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Flashes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:10.21,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're going to capture Akeuchi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.64,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I need to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:15.22,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-She's wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:18.97,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:25.35,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,W-We just happened to stumble upon \Nthat lighthouse after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:29.17,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was the one who insisted that we go in,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.50,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,e-even though Akeuchi-san didn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:35.25,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,S-So, it's not Akeuchi-san's fault, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:36.49,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:37.95,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:40.10,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akeuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:42.57,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-It'll be fine, s-so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:45.80,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for asking such a weird question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.96,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It must have taken you by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:52.33,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I thought for sure that you two \Nwere lighthouse connoisseurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:53.22,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:59.72,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That lighthouse was abandoned ages ago, \Nso no one comes to visit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:03.04,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,But it's always been a favorite spot of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:05.73,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping that you two \Nmight have felt the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.29,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.61,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Your favorite...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:12.05,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, we'll advertise it \Nto everyone out in space!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:14.96,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's turn it into Earth's most \Npopular tourist destination!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:16.49,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you lived there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:19.12,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.12,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}did{\i0} say you're an alien, Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:25.12,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You believe me when I say I'm an alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.37,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:30.40,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to speak with an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.90,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,All of humanity yearns to make \Ncontact with extraterrestrials!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:40.56,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Earthlings and aliens, joining hands \Nto bring about a peaceful universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:41.38,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:44.48,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It truly is the ultimate \Ndream of all living beings—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.83,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,the light of hope that shines eternal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:49.00,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you two agree?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:51.54,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I totally get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.15,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.2\fs22\fnComic Sans MS\c&H1C1317&\pos(184,13)}Doesn't get it at all
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:53.65,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Haruno!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:56.15,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan! Umika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.41,Default,Group,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:01.66,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takaragi-san, I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:04.45,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I, um, had the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:05.54,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:09.79,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy that I got \Nto talk to you, Umika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:11.91,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:14.50,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,U-U-Um, also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:24.42,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much for always \Nsaying hello, and for helping me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:25.41,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:27.70,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,The pleasure is all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:33.12,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It occurred to me during class...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:37.27,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Umika-chan, your voice is so lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:44.69,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Like sweet whispers from crashing waves, \Ntrapped deep inside a tiny seashell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.24,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Dear God!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:53.64,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the wonderful meetings and \Nblessings you have given me on this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:58.93,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I pray that our future may shine \Nas bright as the Milky Way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:02.14,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Haruno, you really get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.30,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.2\fs22\fnComic Sans MS\c&H1C1317&\pos(218,2)}Really doesn't get it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:06.04,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think it'd \Nbe okay to tell Haruno?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:08.28,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the promise we made to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:10.03,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:11.19,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.81,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You see, truth be told,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:17.83,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,we're gonna build a rocket \Nto take us to outer space!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.82,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,She said it out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.27,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:23.32,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Heh heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:28.08,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,What now? What now? What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.58,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:33.38,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The more, the merrier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.67,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,So let's build it together, Haruno!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:39.10,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:41.07,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.37,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.81,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Haruno's one of us, starting today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:48.96,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work together, Umika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:51.84,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,And we can talk even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:53.93,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's one step toward our dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:56.57,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all make the ultimate rocket together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.16,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.82,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san is so amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:07.83,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm with her, it feels like I can \Ndo everything that I couldn't do alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.68,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,It really is so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:14.41,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we're friends, \NI wanted to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:18.24,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That foreheadpathy that you two always do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:20.04,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:20.93,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,"Always"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:21.97,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:25.97,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She was watching us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:28.97,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(776,1)\fnVerdana\c&H82A6E6&\frz4.74\fax-0.06\fsp2.4\pos(483.5,85)}S{\c&HF57A71&}ta{\c&HD5FC8B&}r{\c&H9958ED&}du{\c&HD6FF80&}st {\c&H82A6E6&}Te{\c&HD6FF80&}le{\c&H9958ED&}pa{\c&HF57A71&}th
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.23,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs13\fnTimes New Roman\bord2.5\an8\c&H37AAD3&\3c&H5A4655&\pos(30,235.5)}Visual Encyclopedia of Space Rockets\N{\c&H87A1D5&\3c&H100B16&}Everything About Thrilling Space Rockets\N{\c&H020535&\3c&H788ECE&}Understanding Space   {\c&H8F91CC&\3c&H4C2B5E&}Aerospace Research Society
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.98,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\fnComic Sans MS\b0\c&HAFAFC3&\frz15.3\pos(269.5,28.5)}Takaragi-san is going to help us\Nbuild a rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:39.48,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with a big rocket sounds hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.48,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs24\fnArial Black\shad1.5\bord2\c&HA7F7FD&\3c&H90737F&}Visual Encyclopedia of Space Rockets\N{\c&HF6FFF2&\3c&H431EDF&\fs18}Third Edition
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:43.49,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd rather build something simple first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:45.49,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,This one's definitely not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.99,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,This one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.99,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I bet we could make this, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:50.76,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,"For toddlers"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:52.15,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:53.00,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.88,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I see! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:57.36,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's see, materials...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:12.70,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Ake—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:14.02,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.69,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:18.27,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Recharging my space energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:20.75,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,Sunbathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.32,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.53,Default,Kagami,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:29.91,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:32.66,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.93,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Yu Akeuchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.92,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who didn't \Nhand in that assignment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:41.00,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me to the teachers' office!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.75,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't find the right time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:48.43,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,No! I need to bring it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.51,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:53.89,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.81,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Did she leave already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.10,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.88,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Umika?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.06,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Umika-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:05.18,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:08.20,Default,Group,0000,0000,0000,,A soda-bottle rocket?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:09.60,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:13.37,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be hard to start \Noff by making a real rocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:16.91,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,s-so I found instructions on how \Nto build one of these online.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.89,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,This way, we can all make it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.43,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Show me! Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.73,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I remember making one in grade school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:25.21,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,That takes me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:29.22,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Earth drinks can \Nbe used to make rockets!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:36.22,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.2\fs16\shad1\bord2\fnGeorgia\c&HA0B3BD&\3c&H0D4024&\frz21.31\fax0.04\pos(220.5,108.5)}Take it Tea-sy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:32.88,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how hot tea in \Nvending machines works?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.73,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You're a little off the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:36.22,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,More than a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:37.52,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:38.98,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,With just water and air?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:40.00,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:43.06,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It flies thanks to the air \Npressure inside the bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:46.43,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,The flight distance varies with size, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:52.27,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I believe larger bottles fly farther \Nbecause you can pump more air into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:52.98,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:55.24,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,A big one! Let's make a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:58.00,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she'd say that, so I brought this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.28,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You go, Umika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:00.62,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,So Umi-cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:04.53,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,But these were the only big ones \Nwe had in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:07.53,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I see. We need more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:10.08,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:12.31,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I can gulp this down in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:15.89,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:19.26,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:20.39,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1C1C19&\frz353.7\pos(346.5,28.5)\4c&H23F6FB&}Materials\N\N{\fs20\shad1.5}1. Soda bottle (1.5 L)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:22.58,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we need two more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:23.91,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Two more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.53,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll do it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:30.37,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like fizzy drinks, \Nbut I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:32.41,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a minute, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:34.66,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\fnArial Black\bord4\c&HC3FF4A&\3c&HFDFFFD&}Please wait for just a moment.
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.53,0:15:34.66,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\fnArial Black\bord2\c&HC3FF4A&\3c&H97752F&}Please wait for just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.47,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Michi-chan. Tomo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:38.64,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,How about some soda?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:39.68,Default,Yao,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:40.89,Default,Endo,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.69,Default,Ozaki,0000,0000,0000,,Haruno! I'll have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:44.14,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:46.54,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who's got club, \Nfeel free to take some!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:48.46,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.25,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:50.55,Default,Classmate,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:55.72,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,We should have done this from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:00.02,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's get cracking on this rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.19,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.44,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:06.66,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,F-First, we use a knife \Nto cut the bottle open.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:07.76,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.14,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at this, Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:10.82,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,What a clean cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:13.43,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Umika-chan, you're so \Nskilled with your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:14.23,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:16.20,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Me too! I wanna try too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.12,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:18.41,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.82,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:25.92,DefaultItalics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Umika-chan's face turned redder than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:28.17,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,O-Once we have our parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:32.42,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,next, w-we put it all together like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:35.74,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I brought lots of kinds of colored tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:37.68,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:43.61,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Akeuchi-san look so focused!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:46.19,DefaultItalics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,The rocket is looking stranger by the minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:48.48,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:49.94,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:50.76,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:52.92,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we launch our rocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:57.18,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The sports teams are using the fields...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.35,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,The lighthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.20,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go to the lighthouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.71,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Nice idea, Haruno!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.52,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You could say the lighthouse \Nis the {\i1}right{\i0} house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.86,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Another nice idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:14.22,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket! Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.79,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,And Haruno's with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:18.72,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Off to the lighthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:21.97,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Will it fly properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:23.63,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Fly! Fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:26.14,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Off to space we go-go-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:29.23,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Do aliens like to sing as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:30.61,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:34.56,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling of a melody \Nwelling up in your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:36.61,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's the same across the universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:40.99,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not that I can remember \Nthe songs from my own planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.33,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.00,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me some Earth songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:44.64,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:45.75,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.00,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Umika-chan filling the air with her singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:53.51,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's akin to a rippling sigh from a \Nlily-of-the-valley on a clear morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:58.76,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,You place the rocket on this launchpad,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.95,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,and when you squeeze this handle,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:02.48,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,i-it'll go flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:05.34,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how far will this thing fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:06.64,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:10.55,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,It'll fly pretty far. \NAbout a hundred meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:11.90,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred meters?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:15.32,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Which planets are in that range?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.28,DefaultItalics,Group,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to go to space with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:21.84,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think a bottle rocket will \Nbe quite enough to reach outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:22.80,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:24.54,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's disappointed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.54,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:31.04,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't remember my home planet \Nor why I came to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:34.32,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sure what I'd do \Nif we really went to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:36.92,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm a little relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:40.80,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's still lots \NI wanna learn about Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.18,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,And about the two of you, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:48.04,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Though I feel like I've gotten a pretty \Ngood grasp on you, Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:50.69,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Foreheadpathy up close!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.08,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:56.94,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Is it weird that I feel relieved \Nthat I can't go back to space?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:19:00.20,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I, for one, think it's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:04.95,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:08.44,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and fill the rocket up with water!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:09.87,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:15.46,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Yu-chan has \Ntaken a liking to this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:17.73,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Umika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:22.30,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,If you went to outer space, and you \Nmet some aliens, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:27.97,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I want to escape the oppression \Nand agony of Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.59,0:19:31.48,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,and make friends with aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.23,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,In my case,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:37.86,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I want everyone to find out, \Nlike Yu-chan did,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:41.36,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,about the wonderful places \Nand people on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:47.02,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Takaragi-san's unclouded words,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:52.44,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,for someone like me, who thought of \Nnothing but escaping this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:55.80,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,came as a breath of fresh air, as a shock,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:58.65,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,and as a brilliant flash that \Nseared itself into my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:03.51,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel a prickling in my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:08.39,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that she'll look back on \Ntoday as a wonderful memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:11.42,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:17.68,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:19.04,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,We're good to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:21.53,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You two, let's all grab the handle together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:23.14,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:26.24,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's count down and press the \Nlaunch button all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:27.23,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:28.25,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:29.41,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.10,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:33.60,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's our second step toward our dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.67,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies! Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.08,DefaultTop,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:38.63,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Our dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:38.63,DefaultTop,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:39.67,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:41.57,Default,Group,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.80,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:01.19,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,We really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:02.88,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:08.14,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,the prickling in my chest, amidst the \Ncountless sparkles that surrounded me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:10.70,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,melted away into nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:16.35,Narration,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps this was the wonderful feeling \Nthat Takaragi-san mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:17.96,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:19.68,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's launch it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:22.22,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Um, unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:23.74,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,the rocket landed in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:24.97,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:28.66,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I really liked that design, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:30.96,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to go get it back somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.96,0:21:32.60,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I have a net!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.49,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you think that flew \Na hundred meters just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:37.73,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,We should measure it next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:44.71,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,It's sparkling.
