Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:19.22,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.56,0:23:22.46,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:25.21,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\blur0.2\fs32\c&H121714&\pos(320,44)}"Friend, comrade"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:25.21,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\blur0.2\fs30\c&H121714&\pos(320,200)}Tomoraav
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:27.58,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
